PlaceholderDesc_Object: Object to which the language file belongs.
PlaceholderDesc_LanguageKeys: List of language keys that are being exported. Can be iterated using for. The property of the entries can be found under cur_key.
PlaceholderDesc_ReferencedLanguageKeys: List of language keys that are being referenced by the current object (i.e. if a quest is used in the dialog). Can be iterated using for. The property of the entries can be found under cur_key.
